# Architettura — Live SLIDE CENTER

## Stack Tecnologico

| Layer | Tecnologia | Versione |
|-------|-----------|----------|
| Frontend web | React 19 + TypeScript strict | latest |
| Build | Vite 8 | latest |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 4 + shadcn/ui + Radix | latest |
| Routing | React Router 7 | latest |
| State | Zustand | latest |
| Table | TanStack Table | latest |
| Form | Zod + React Hook Form | latest |
| i18n | i18next + react-i18next | latest |
| Upload | tus-js-client + use-tus | latest |
| Backend/DB | Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime + Edge Functions + Storage) | latest |
| Desktop Agent | Tauri v2 + Axum (Rust) + SQLite (rusqlite) | latest |
| Desktop Player | Tauri v2 (leggero) | latest |
| Monorepo | Turborepo + pnpm | latest |

